Let the games begin

<p>
We're pleased to announce our new publicly-facing MAME/MESS SVN server located at: svn://dspnet.fr/mame/trunk<br/>
<br/>
When contributing code, please base your changes on the latest code found on the SVN server.<br/><br/>
We will continue to create patches and releases as before, but our hope is that this will provide better communication with end users and potential contributors.<br/>
